0uNvsKDLg&oe=66EAB8C0"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Untitled15.png", "id": "533743952653806", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031480_533743955987139_1131654148368741799_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bkXd_s63FBgQ7kNvgHrnZ_4&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AEg66Suh6mYA41H6x4KWKtf&oh=00_AYAb7mHj3sFUBf9gcdE9wz_Hy1TNDbsEDERHp_d0InKJ-Q&oe=66EAAA1D"}, "display_name": "EarthQuest", "keywords": ["earth", "fly", "travel", "explore", "world"], "long_description": "( NO Setup needed before use )\n\n**3D Coverage Everywhere**\n\n\u2022 Almost every recognizable city on earth is available in True 3D, even my tiny town in a poor side of Romania is covered, so you are likely able to visit your own street in 3D\n\n**ChatGPT Integration: The AI companion can**\n\n\u2022 Naturally respond in YOUR OWN Language\n\n\u2022 Visualize & understand your surroundings for any educational purpose or to simply give fun facts\n\n\u2022 Teleport you anywhere on earth if asked\n\n.. and more\n\n**Street View**\n\n\u2022 Best UNCOMPRESSED 8k Quality on the market, with every street 360 and community panorama on earth\n\n**Realistic Graphics**\n\n\u2022 Real Life Inspired Lighting based on the Customizable Day/Night Cycle\n\n**Multiplayer**\n\n\u2022 Explore alongside a friend\n\n**Hand Tracking**\n\n\u2022 Fly like a Superhero by pointing your index finger\n\n\u2022 Rotate by Turning an Imaginary Steering Wheel\n\n**Terrain Quality**\n\n\u2022 The 3D Map Quality can go much further than anything else out there and achieve realistic 3D by pushing the map quality to extreme detail with the best possible performance\n\n**Comfort Settings**\n\n\u2022 Comfort Options ( Snap Turning / Flight Vignette ) to prevent Motion Sickness\n\n\u2022 Button Remapping ( Flight Controls Range from Simple to Complex Cinematic Flying )\n\n**Google Maps Integration**\n\n\u2022 Auto / manual zoom based on altitude\n\n\u2022 Paired with the compass for body orientation\n\n\u2022 Full Google Maps functionality on the Map Window feature\n\n**.. out of space, check \"earthquest.site\" ..**", "short_description": "The ENTIRE Earth in True 3D, and every 360 on the planet in 8k - ( The Best Street View Quality on the Market )\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\nfor more info, see:\nearthquest.site"}]}, "developer_name": "Boe", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/earthquestvr/home/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/earthquestvr/home/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "Boe", "support_website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/earthquestvr/home/contact", "website_url": "http://earthquest.site/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1067126693731825"}, {"id": "879473995923081"}, {"id": "726368587961803"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING", "SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "7962896583840005"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031503_1532297684019289_3733568735121312725_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UVOrJ_JSvMwQ7kNvgGwCniw&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AEg66Suh6mYA41H6x4KWKtf&oh=00_AYA5ezJncGP_FB8da6mPGOOPA2y3BAGfE5CNyPaZJY8paQ&oe=66EAA670"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "EarthQuest", "platform"